name: rosdistro
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "rosdistro" %}
{% set version = "0.8.3" %}
{% set sha256 = "ecdf3fc85a1aced74950d8bf8946509d841aa846277789c037ac38e11ed67e2e" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/ros-infrastructure/{{ name }}/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 4
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - python                                 # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - cross-python_{{ target_platform }}     # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - pyyaml
    - catkin_pkg
    - rospkg

test:
  commands:
    - rosdistro_build_cache --help
    - rosdistro_freeze_source --help
    - rosdistro_migrate_to_rep_141 --help
    - rosdistro_migrate_to_rep_143 --help
    - rosdistro_reformat --help
  imports:
    - rosdistro

about:
  home: http://wiki.ros.org/rosdistro
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: Tools to work with catkinized rosdistro files
  dev_url: https://github.com/ros-infrastructure/rosdistro

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - wolfv
    - lesteve
    - seanyen
